ETa - EPCIS Trusted Agent

Capabilities and permissions policy agent for EPCIS.

ETa/                        agent of access control
EpcisPHI/                   permissions management web application
ETa-Callback/               modules of callback management
ETa-Capture-Client/         client library for the capture service
ETa-Query-Client/           client library for the Query service
LibXACML-EPCIS/             XACML library

Usage Dependencies:
  - a MySQL server
  - a LDAP server
  - a JMS/ActiveMQ server
  - an EPCIS

Installation and Configuration:
  IoTa-Installer installs and configures ETa.
  The script ldap.sh allows you to configure the group usergroup and to add
  two users: superadmin and anonymous to your LDAP server.

Usage:
  see ALfA for examples
